    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>Participants will be referred to the Michigan Surgical &amp; Health Optimization Program in the month leading up to their surgery. Individuals are encouraged to increase their physical activity, practice stress reduction, and other behaviors associated with good health.</description>
  </arm_group>
